`ОЈ_{Пғвү 1} v_Q(Оё вҲ’ ПғОё) = ОЈ_{iвүҘ0} (#G_i вҲ’ 1)` (IV В§1 Prop. 4 and
Lemme 1); completion invariance of the different (III В§4 Prop. 10)
carries the divisibility back to the global `рқ”Ў_{K/в„ҡ}`. -/
theorem pow_sum_card_inertia_dvd_differentIdeal
    (K : IntermediateField в„ҡ (AlgebraicClosure в„ҡ)) [NumberField K]
    [IsGalois в„ҡ K]
    (Q : Ideal (NumberField.RingOfIntegers K)) (hQ : Q.IsPrime)
    (hQbot : Q вү  вҠҘ) (n : в„•) :
    Q ^ (вҲ‘ i вҲҲ Finset.range n,
        (Nat.card ((Q ^ (i + 1)).inertia (K вүғвӮҗ[в„ҡ] K)) - 1)) вҲЈ
      differentIdeal в„Ө (NumberField.RingOfIntegers K) :=
  sorry

