/-- **Fontaine's different bound for a finite flat Hopf order over
`в„ӨвӮғ` killed by `3`** (sorry node, created 2026-07-24 вҖ” the
scheme-theoretic core of the localized Fontaine leaf, now stated
PURELY in the project's finite-flat vocabulary вҖ” an explicit finite
