`exists_connectedEtale_subgroup_of_hopf_package` below, with NO
representation-theoretic input left; Fontaine, *Il n'y a pas de
variГ©tГ© abГ©lienne sur в„Ө*, Invent. Math. 81 (1985), Thm. A and В§В§1вҖ“3;
MoonвҖ“Taguchi, Doc. Math. Extra Vol. Kato (2003), В§2): if every
geometric point `ПҮ : в„ҡвӮғбөҘ вҠ— G вҶ’вӮҗ в„ҡвӮғбөҘбөғЛЎбөҚ` is killed by `3` in the
convolution group (`hkill` вҖ” the scheme-level "`G` is killed by `3`"
follows for the flat `G` from its generic fibre), then every finite
subextension `M` of `в„ҡвӮғбөғЛЎбөҚ/в„ҡвӮғ` contained in the field
`L = в„ҡвӮғ(G(в„ҡвӮғбөғЛЎбөҚ))` generated by the points вҖ” the containment
expressed Galois-theoretically by `hM`: every substitution fixing all
