/-- **Fontaine's sharp different-exponent bound at a choosable prime
over `3`** (DECOMPOSED 2026-07-24 into the two sorry nodes above вҖ”
the LOCAL Fontaine bound
`two_mul_local_differentIdeal_exponent_add_two_le_of_flat_at_three`
(where the flatness input `hПҒ.isFlat` genuinely lives, now a purely
local statement about finite subextensions of `в„ҡвӮғбөғЛЎбөҚ/в„ҡвӮғ`) and the
distinguished-prime/completion-invariance passage
`exists_prime_over_three_of_local_different_bound` (pure algebraic
number theory) вҖ” with the kernel-field glue PROVEN here: `hfix`
identifies `K.fixingSubgroup` with `ker u`, so a subextension fixed
by every substitution fixing `K` is fixed by every substitution
killed by `u`, i.e. lies in the local kernel field `в„ҡвӮғ(V)`, which is
exactly the containment the local leaf consumes): SOME prime `QвӮҖ` of
`рқ“һ K` above `3` вҖ” the distinguished prime induced by the fixed
embedding `О№ : в„ҡбөғЛЎбөҚ вҶ’ в„ҡвӮғбөғЛЎбөҚ` вҖ” satisfies the SHARP different-exponent
bound `2В·d + 2 вүӨ 3В·e(QвӮҖвҲЈ3)` for every `d` with `QвӮҖ^d вҲЈ рқ”Ў_{K/в„ҡ}`.
This strengthens by the `+2` the bound of the (downstream, proven)
`exists_prime_over_three_differentIdeal_exponent_bound`; it is
strictly upstream of that chain, so no circularity.  Mathematical
content (Fontaine 1985, Thm. A/В§3; MoonвҖ“Taguchi 2003, В§2): the
completion of `K` at the distinguished prime is `M := в„ҡвӮғ(О№ K) =
в„ҡвӮғ(V)`, generated by the points of the finite flat group scheme
`G/в„ӨвӮғ` killed by `3` prolonging the local representation, and
Fontaine's theorem bounds `v_M(рқ”Ў_{M/в„ҡвӮғ}) вүӨ (3/2)В·e вҲ’ 1`.  Sharpness:
the peu-ramifiГ© kernel field `в„ҡвӮғ(О¶вӮғ, u^{1/3})` has `e = 6`,
`v(рқ”Ў) = 8`, attaining equality `2В·8 + 2 = 18 = 3В·6`. -/
theorem exists_prime_over_three_differentIdeal_exponent_fontaine_bound
    {k : Type u} [Finite k] [Field k]
    [Algebra в„Ө_[3] k] [TopologicalSpace k] [DiscreteTopology k]
    (V : Type*) [AddCommGroup V] [Module k V] [Module.Finite k V]
    [Module.Free k V]
    (hV : Module.rank k V = 2) {ПҒ : GaloisRep в„ҡ k V}
    (hПҒ : IsHardlyRamified (show Odd 3 by decide) hV ПҒ)
    (b : Module.Basis (Fin 2) (AlgebraicClosure k)
      ((AlgebraicClosure k) вҠ—[k] V))
    (e : AlgebraicClosure k вүғ+* Dickson.K 3)
    (u : О“ в„ҡ вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) (Dickson.K 3))
    (hu : вҲҖ g, ((u g : GL (Fin 2) (Dickson.K 3)) :
      Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) (Dickson.K 3)) =
      (LinearMap.toMatrix b b ((Slop.OddRep.baseChange (AlgebraicClosure k)
        (MonoidHomClass.toMonoidHom ПҒ)) g)).map e)
    (K : IntermediateField в„ҡ (AlgebraicClosure в„ҡ)) [NumberField K]
    [IsGalois в„ҡ K] (hfix : K.fixingSubgroup = u.ker) :
    вҲғ (QвӮҖ : Ideal (NumberField.RingOfIntegers K)) (_ : QвӮҖ.IsPrime)
      (_ : ((3 : в„•) : NumberField.RingOfIntegers K) вҲҲ QвӮҖ),
      вҲҖ d : в„•, QвӮҖ ^ d вҲЈ differentIdeal в„Ө (NumberField.RingOfIntegers K) вҶ’
