`Ideal.ramificationIdx_eq_of_isGaloisGroup` as in the proven transport
below) вҖ” SOME prime `QвӮҖ` of `рқ“һ K` above `3` satisfies the
different-exponent bound `2В·d вүӨ 3В·e(QвӮҖвҲЈ3)` for every `d` with
