В§В§3вҖ“5), the natural further decomposition of this leaf:

1. *Ideal lattices and their duals* (Neukirch VII В§3).  Choose an
   integral ideal `рқ”һ вҲҲ CвҒ»В№`; the nonzero integral ideals in `C`
   biject with the `рқ’Ә_K^Г—`-orbits of nonzero elements of `рқ”һ`
