/-- **The induced eigenvalue character is conjugation-symmetric вҖ” the
per-quadratic-field ray-class computation** (sorry node, isolated
2026-07-23 from `dihedral_induced_ray_class_of_two_unramified` below,
whose linear-algebra layer вҖ” the second eigenline and the determinant
identity вҖ” is PROVEN glue there): the eigenvalue character `ПҮвӮҖ` of
