/-- **The dihedral ray-class core for the induced eigenvalue
character** (DECOMPOSED 2026-07-23 into the two sorry nodes above вҖ”
the local-at-`2` unipotence analysis
`induced_character_unramified_at_two` and the at-`3`/ray-class
computation `dihedral_induced_ray_class_of_two_unramified`; the
assembly is proven): the per-field class-field-theoretic core of the
dihedral case, with the whole induced-representation step hoisted
into PROVEN hypotheses вҖ” `ПҮвӮҖ` is the eigenvalue character of the
common eigenline `KВ·v` of `u` on `H := ker Оё' = О“_{в„ҡ(вҲҡd)}`,
multiplicative (`hПҮmul`), nonvanishing (`hПҮne0`), trivial on `ker ПҒ`
(`hПҮker`, so its kernel is OPEN), trivial on the inertia of every
prime `q вҲү {2, 3}` (`hПҮunr`); the second line `KВ·(u ПғвӮҖ В·бөҘ v)` is
independent (`hindep`); and `hne` says that `ПҮвӮҖ` differs from its
`ПғвӮҖ`-conjugate on `H`, i.e. `ПҒ вү… Ind_H^{О“_в„ҡ} ПҮвӮҖ` genuinely
dihedrally. -/
theorem dihedral_induced_character_ray_class {k : Type u}
    [Finite k] [Field k]
    [Algebra в„Ө_[3] k] [TopologicalSpace k] [DiscreteTopology k]
    (V : Type*) [AddCommGroup V] [Module k V] [Module.Finite k V]
    [Module.Free k V]
    (hV : Module.rank k V = 2) {ПҒ : GaloisRep в„ҡ k V}
    (hПҒ : IsHardlyRamified (show Odd 3 by decide) hV ПҒ)
    (habs : Slop.OddRep.IsAbsolutelyIrreducible
      (MonoidHomClass.toMonoidHom ПҒ : Representation k (О“ в„ҡ) V))
    (b : Module.Basis (Fin 2) (AlgebraicClosure k)
      ((AlgebraicClosure k) вҠ—[k] V))
    (e : AlgebraicClosure k вүғ+* Dickson.K 3)
    (u : О“ в„ҡ вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) (Dickson.K 3))
    (hu : вҲҖ g, ((u g : GL (Fin 2) (Dickson.K 3)) :
      Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) (Dickson.K 3)) =
      (LinearMap.toMatrix b b ((Slop.OddRep.baseChange (AlgebraicClosure k)
        (MonoidHomClass.toMonoidHom ПҒ)) g)).map e)
    (Оё' : О“ в„ҡ вҶ’* Multiplicative (ZMod 2))
    (hОё'surj : Function.Surjective Оё')
    (htriv' : вҲҖ g : О“ в„ҡ, ПҒ g = 1 вҶ’ Оё' g = 1)
    (v : Fin 2 вҶ’ Dickson.K 3) (hv : v вү  0)
    (d : в„Ө)
    (hd : d = -1 вҲЁ d = 2 вҲЁ d = -2 вҲЁ d = 3 вҲЁ d = -3 вҲЁ d = 6 вҲЁ d = -6)
    (x : AlgebraicClosure в„ҡ) (hx : x ^ 2 = (d : AlgebraicClosure в„ҡ))
    (hОё'x : вҲҖ g : О“ в„ҡ, Оё' g = 1 вҶ” g x = x)
    (ПғвӮҖ : О“ в„ҡ) (hПғвӮҖ : Оё' ПғвӮҖ вү  1)
    (ПҮвӮҖ : О“ в„ҡ вҶ’ Dickson.K 3)
    (hПҮвӮҖ : вҲҖ g : О“ в„ҡ, Оё' g = 1 вҶ’
      Matrix.mulVec ((u g : GL (Fin 2) (Dickson.K 3)) :
        Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) (Dickson.K 3)) v = ПҮвӮҖ g вҖў v)
    (hПҮne0 : вҲҖ g : О“ в„ҡ, Оё' g = 1 вҶ’ ПҮвӮҖ g вү  0)
    (hПҮmul : вҲҖ g h : О“ в„ҡ, Оё' g = 1 вҶ’ Оё' h = 1 вҶ’
      ПҮвӮҖ (g * h) = ПҮвӮҖ g * ПҮвӮҖ h)
    (hПҮker : вҲҖ g : О“ в„ҡ, ПҒ g = 1 вҶ’ ПҮвӮҖ g = 1)
    (hПҮunr : вҲҖ (q : в„•) (hq : q.Prime), q вү  2 вҶ’ q вү  3 вҶ’
      вҲҖ Пғ вҲҲ localInertiaGroup hq.toHeightOneSpectrumRingOfIntegersRat,
        ПҮвӮҖ (Field.absoluteGaloisGroup.map (algebraMap в„ҡ
          (IsDedekindDomain.HeightOneSpectrum.adicCompletion в„ҡ
            hq.toHeightOneSpectrumRingOfIntegersRat)) Пғ) = 1)
    (hindep : В¬ вҲғ c : Dickson.K 3,
      Matrix.mulVec ((u ПғвӮҖ : GL (Fin 2) (Dickson.K 3)) :
        Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) (Dickson.K 3)) v = c вҖў v)
    (hne : В¬ вҲҖ g : О“ в„ҡ, Оё' g = 1 вҶ’ ПҮвӮҖ g = ПҮвӮҖ (ПғвӮҖвҒ»В№ * g * ПғвӮҖ)) :
    False :=
  dihedral_induced_ray_class_of_two_unramified V hV hПҒ habs b e u hu Оё'
    hОё'surj htriv' v hv d hd x hx hОё'x ПғвӮҖ hПғвӮҖ ПҮвӮҖ hПҮвӮҖ hПҮne0 hПҮmul hПҮker
    hПҮunr hindep
    (induced_character_unramified_at_two V hV hПҒ b e u hu Оё' htriv' v hv
