    В· refine вҹЁОҪ, LinearMap.ext fun v => ?_вҹ©
      have hv : v вҲҲ Module.End.eigenspace T ОҪ := hE в–ё Submodule.mem_top
      rw [Module.End.mem_eigenspace_iff] at hv
      simpa using hv
